HEADWORD: Contributor
<hw>Con*trib"u*tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or
that which, contributes;</def> <specif>specifically,</specif> <def>one
who writes articles for a newspaper, magazine, or book.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

